Description: Provides tools for hydrological frequency analysis, including
    exploratory summaries, distribution fitting, return-level estimation,
    bootstrap confidence intervals, goodness-of-fit assessment, sample
    diagnostics, AI-assisted distribution-selection support, batch workflows,
    publication-ready plots, and export helpers.
